wwv_flow_api.create_message(
 p_id=>wwv_flow_api.id(1450666592575430488)
,p_name=>'HELP_GETTING_STARTED'
,p_message_text=>wwv_flow_string.join(wwv_flow_t_varchar2(
'<div class="textRegion">',
'<h2>Getting Started</h2>',
'<h3>1. Create a survey</h3>',
'<p>Before you begin identify the research objectives, the population, and the sampling method.</p>',
'<ul>',
'<li>Click Surveys in the navigation men</li>',
'<li>Click the Create Survey button and follow the wizard prompts</li>',
'<li>From the Surveys report click the name of the survey you just created to view its details</li>',
'<li>On the survey details page click the Edit link on the questionnaire region title bar</li>',
'<li>On the questionnaire editing page, add sections, questions, and answers to create the questionnaire</li>',
'<li>Click the preview button to see what the questionnaire will look like when respondents fill it out</li>',
'<li>You can control how the questionnaire looks by clicking on the Format Options button and changing settings</li>',
'<li>If the survey will be distributed by email click the Manage Email button on the survey details page',
'and create one or more emails. Emails can be sent to request a respondent participate in the survey, ',
'remind respondents if they haven''''t responded within a given number of days ',
'and to thank the respondent when they complete the questionnaire.',
'Note: An administrator must configure the From email address on the Email Configuration page before emails can be sent.</li>',
'</ul>',
'<h3>2. Test</h3>',
'<p>Once you create a survey and its questionnaire you will want to test it on a few test subjects to',
'get feedback on the understandability, appropriateness and completeness of the questions and answer choices.</p>',
'<ul>',
'<li>On the survey details page click the Begin Testing button</li>',
'<li>If this is a random sample survey each respondent gets their own unique code. You can choose to have Survey Builder',
'send emails with the unique questionnaire URL to specific respondents or manually distribute the URLs. ',
'If the distribution method is manual enter the number of respondents. If the distribution method is email',
'enter the email addresses of the test subjects.</li>',
'<li>If this is a self selected survey then there is one URL to the questionnaire for anyone.</li>',
'<li>Click the Begin Test button</li>',
'<li>Click Manage Respondents button on the survey details page to get the self-select URL, or',
'see a list of respondents and their specific URLs.</li>',
'<li>When testing is complete click the Complete Testing button on the survey details. Then you can ',
'edit the questionnaire based on any feedback received from the test subjects.</li>',
'</ul>',
'<h3>3. Begin the survey</h3>',
'<p>Once the questionnaire is exactly the way you want it is time to start the survey.</p>',
'<ul>',
'<li>On the survey details page click the Begin Survey button</li>',
'<li>If this is a random sample survey each respondent gets their own unique code. You can choose to have Survey Builder',
'send emails with the unique questionnaire URL to specific respondents or manually distribute the URLs.',
'If the distribution method is manual enter the number of respondents (this defaults to the Sample Size).',
'If the distribution method is email enter the email addresses of the respondents.</li>',
'<li>If this is a self selected survey then there is one URL to the questionnaire for anyone.</li>',
'<li>Click the Begin Survey button</li>',
'<li>Click Manage Respondents button on the survey details page to get the self-select URL, or',
'see a list of respondents and their specific URLs. This also tracks which emails have been sent. ',
'You can add more respondents after the survey has started.</li>',
'<li>If the survey has Target Date and/or Target Percent set and Auto Complete is Yes then within a day',
'of the target date passing or receiving target percent of responses the survey will be complete. You ',
'can also manually complete the survey at any time by clicking the Complete Survey button on the survey details page.',
'Once complete no new responses will be accepted.</li>',
'<li>View and analyze response data using the reports available from the survey details page.</li>',
'</ul>',
'</div>'))
);
